<item>
            <title>[LU-11282] osd-zfs to discard cache quickly if configured</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11282</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;osd-ldiskfs has an option to discard buffers (pagecache) right after processing. this can be useful in cases when data is not reused generally.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;osd-zfs should provide a similar capability.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
